Class::Observable - Base class for observable classes/objects
=============================

INSTALLATION

To install this module perform the typical four-part Perl salute:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Class::ISA

